---

âš™ Setup Instructions

1. Clone the Repository

git clone https://github.com/yourusername/rationchain.git
cd rationchain

2. Smart Contracts

cd contracts
npm install
npx hardhat compile

3. Backend Setup

cd ../backend
npm install

Create a .env file:

PORT=3000
MONGO_URI=your_mongodb_uri
JWT_SECRET=your_jwt_secret
CHAINLINK_API_KEY=optional_if_used

Run backend server:

npm run dev

4. Frontend Setup

cd ../frontend
npm install
npm start


